[Cheshbonos]

* Cheshbonos: This is Cheshbonos, a tool for improving Gemara skills. At the moment Cheshbonos offers help in learning [[Perek Ha'ish Mekadesh]]. You can [[navigate by mouse and arrow keys]]. Cheshbonos is published with various [[disclaimers]]. You can post your questions or comments on the [issues page](https://github.com/cheshbonos/cheshbonos/issues). Sign up for occasional [[email updates]]. Cheshbonos is built using [Canopy.js](https://github.com/canopy-js/canopy-js).
